ghosts (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release of ghosts v2.
  * 9 animated scenes: Ghost, MatrixRain, RainDrops, Plasma, TopoFlyover,
    GlitchScreen, BioScan, ComputerSim, Switchboard.
  * Notcurses-inspired z-ordered plane compositor.
  * Ghost scene captures live tmux pane content before launch.
  * Switchboard includes interactive Shadytel exchange and PANIC crash mode.

